    <h2>WHAT INFORMATION WE COLLECT</h2>

    <h3>Information Provided By You</h3>

    <p>In order for you to register as a user and access certain portions of our Sourcery Platform and/or participate in certain services, and if you communicate with us by e-mail or otherwise complete online forms or the like, we may require you to provide us with information that personally identifies you, such as your name, mailing address, e-mail address and home and/or business telephone numbers, bank account number, credit card or debit card number, as well as any account number that we assign to you ("Personal Information") which may be retained and used by us as described in this Privacy Policy.</p>

